sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular
    participant GW as Gateway YARP
    participant BE as Writer BE
    participant OAI as OpenAI

    FE->>GW: POST /apps/writer/api/chat with messages and writing_mode
    GW->>GW: SubscriptionMiddleware allows anonymous
    GW->>BE: POST /api/chat after prefix stripped
    BE->>BE: optional_user returns None
    BE->>OAI: chat.completions.create stream=true
    loop tokens
        OAI-->>BE: chunk
        BE-->>FE: data line with token
    end
    BE-->>FE: sources event with empty array
    BE-->>FE: data DONE marker
